{"tid":2195722,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB急抽起《唐人街》 改播《C9特工》","createTime":"2020-09-09T11:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T15:19:33.000Z","uid":80972,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1964ad7e45b0bfee5327a7326af4fe02e3f8797a","tid":2195722,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"[無綫][急抽起《唐人街》 改播《C9特工》] <br />\n<br />\n最新消息，無綫決定抽起已經開始播宣傳片嘅《唐人街》。《反黑路人甲》結局之後，9月21日夜晚2130改播《C9特工》。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">《唐人街》講述1940年代泰國唐人街華人被欺壓，<strong><span class=\"x-large\">眾人團結反抗嘅故事</span></strong></span>，由陳展鵬、伍允龍、陳山聰、唐詩詠、王君馨、姚子羚、元秋等主演。<br />\n<br />\n據悉無綫內部本星期初仍然討論緊《唐人街》宣傳活動，為劇集播放造勢。<br />\n<br />\n《C9特工》由高海寧、馬國明、黎諾懿、朱敏瀚等人參演。連同《殺手》、《反黑路人甲》、《迷網》，高海寧連續於4齣劇擔任重要角色。<br />\n<br />\n#無綫 #TVB #唐人街 #C9特工 #方以文 #fem<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">做咩呀，中共唔俾播呀？</span></span>"},{"pid":"d041909e07089ed5faacba98cb759056ed090e16","tid":2195722,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:01:24.000Z","msg":"汁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1059324757464902/posts/3476474525749901/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1059324757464902%2Fposts%2F3476474525749901%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=6a4b5463\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1059324757464902/posts/3476474525749901/</a>"},{"pid":"df3edd0ce88cc5f1516321c3ad9c95d39e3058c1","tid":2195722,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:03:00.000Z","msg":"仲諗住唔反tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ce42f5e5d5db1dd2e338ebad2f5e7bd41c158d","tid":2195722,"uid":80972,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"呢套野應該咁就打入冷宮<br />\n又唔見幾百萬"},{"pid":"8a0f07f1c5a17e13c85b2e448318aefc0a7b8b85","tid":2195722,"uid":16061,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"rep